				ok, id just like to add something that i did at very low lvl for my smithing. it may be a good idea to save the practice points and make metal bits till trivial from 1 in smithing. that way, theres no runing around looking for rusty weapons, you can use yur practices for other things, and youll have a **** load of metal bits to use for your skewers, scalers, tool boxes, and other things. i dunno if thats the right thing to do but it saved me a lot of frustration at later lvls not havin to make metal bits
