			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				to sharpen rusty stuff, you place the rusty weapon and a sharpening stone in the forge. I'm not sure if you need water you should check Everlore's official guide.<BR>
<BR>
There are two forges in Neriak, one in the foriegn quater in the troll part near a shop with two trolls, one who sells tailoring stuff. There is another in the commons, if you travel towards 3rd gate you will pass it, it is just before neriak underground.<BR>
<BR>
To make studs you need 3 metal bits, a flask of water and a file. You will get your file back fail or suceed, and with the new patch you will recieve 2 studs that are (thank innoruk) stackable.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps<BR>
Artemous, smithing guy
				</font>
			</td>

